Uses of Package
com.vernalis.pdbconnector.config

  • Packages that use com.vernalis.pdbconnector.config 
    Package Description
    com.vernalis.pdbconnector
    This package contains the core KNIME-related classes for the PDB Connector webservice nodes
    com.vernalis.pdbconnector.config
    This package implements (non-KNIME related) classes used to define the query and report options supported by the PDB advanced search and custom report web services.
    com.vernalis.pdbconnector.nodes.pdbconnector
    This package contains the classes for the node implementations for the 2nd Generation PDB Connector node family
